      notion</unclear> in my letter to Fleming. </p>
            <p>Ihope you will <unclear reason="illegible" resp="NW">take </unclear> the <unclear reason="illegible" resp="NW">field</unclear> actively &amp; <unclear reason="illegible" resp="NW">persistently, get olee </unclear> Knox &amp; Sevier <unclear reason="illegible" resp="NW">give rude or vote us out </unclear> be a <unclear reason="illegible" resp="NW">quieter to Dirunium for a time at Court-</unclear>
            </p>
